170
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,600
「please keep your voice down(お静かに願います)」。

171
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,600
「keep your voice down(声を抑えてください)」。

172
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:50,040
